Step 1: Run Jenkins (VERY IMPORTANT)
⚠️ If you are using Windows (like your system)

The command you pasted (/var/run/docker.sock) works only on Linux/macOS.

👉 For Windows, use this:

docker volume create jenkins-data

docker run -d ^
  --name jenkins ^
  -p 8080:8080 -p 50000:50000 ^
  -v jenkins-data:/var/jenkins_home ^
  -v //var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock ^
  jenkins/jenkins:lts
